org.jbiowhcore.utility.fileformats.orthoxml

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbiowhcore.utility.fileformats.orthoxml.Database

  • public class Database
extends Object
    A database element contains all genes from a single database/source.

    Java class for database complex type.

    The following schema fragment specifies the expected content contained within this class. 

     <complexType name="database">
   <complexContent>
     <restriction base="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyType">
       <sequence>
         <element name="genes" type="{http://orthoXML.org/2011/}genes"/>
       </sequence>
       <attribute name="geneLink" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyURI" />
       <attribute name="name" use="required" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}string" />
       <attribute name="protLink" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyURI" />
       <attribute name="transcriptLink" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyURI" />
       <attribute name="version" use="required" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anySimpleType" />
     </restriction>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
